extendedInfo.description: Jiro computer is serving the Laos County and its surrounding provinces for over 6 years. Together,more than 30 of our technician team have over 10years of computer experience in computer services, Notebook repairing,printer hardware repairing and network consulting. Unlike the chain stores, we cater to your needs and provide friendly speedy service. We update our products with a large selections of new notebooks & hi-tech computers every week. we also do custom build computers.We mainly repairing hardwares of Notebooks, camera, LCD Projector,TV, LCD Monitor, Mobile smartphone,Apple products, sony products. We are authorised by SONY Asia Pacific as a Dealera, Authorised Dealer of Samsung Asia Pacific, Authoirsed Service center of Brother Printers, Authorised by Fuji Xerox Japan as service center and distributor in LAO PDR.
